The paper discusses building a trusted reliable distributed service, which falls under the category of security and cryptography (cs.CR). The service is distributed across administrative domains, which involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and distributed systems (cs.Distributed). The paper also discusses the application of the service, which is a public key time stamping service, and the implementation of the service, which involves software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the importance of long-term archival of signed documents, which falls under the category of cyber security (cs.CY).
